CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 15, 1962, pg. 19 reads: "Celebrating - Invited guests smile happily as Deborah Townsend prepares to cut her cake at her tenth birthday party, given her by her parents, the Rev. and Mrs. Gorge Townsend, 3386 Milwaukee St. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of boys and girls, gathered around Deborah Townsend cutting cake at her tenth birthday party, in home of Rev. and Mrs. Gorge Townsend, 3386 Milwaukee Street
